
POST http://localhost:8082/api/admin/product/add
Request:
{
    "productName" : "Apple",
     "description" : "Apple is good",
      "quantity" : "2",
       "price" : "20",
       "rating" : "2"
}

GET http://localhost:8082/api/product -> Get All Products

GET http://localhost:8082/api/product-with-pagination?pageNumber=0&pageSize=3

GET http://localhost:8082/api/product-sorted-by-price-asc-desc?sortBy=productId&sortDir=desc

GET http://localhost:8082/api/product-sorted-by-price-asc-desc?sortBy=productId&sortDir=asc

GET http://localhost:8082/api/product-pagination-sorting?pageNumber=0&pageSize=3&sort=productId, desc